      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Combine your<strong> curry powder</strong>,<strong> ground paprika </strong>and<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with 1/4 of your<strong> natural yoghurt </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s]</strong> – this is your<strong> tandoori marinade</strong></p>",
