    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the naan[s] are in the toaster, chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Cut your<strong> cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>cucumber</strong> to a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato & cucumber salad</strong></p>",
