    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> with your<strong> mint sauce</strong> – this is your <strong>mint yoghurt</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
