            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warmed naan </strong>with the <strong>tandoori king prawns</strong>, <strong>tomato & cucumber salad</strong> and <strong>mint yoghurt</strong> on top</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>nigella seeds</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
